  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7769093/" class="title-link">《心胜》读书摘要</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7769093"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/niro/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1260047-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/niro/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">niro</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-02-12"
      class="main-meta">2016-02-12 01:15:10</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7769093_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  1、人要有点精神，军人最宝贵的精神就是胜利精神。除去胜利一无所求，为了胜利一无所惜，这样的军人是国家和民族的无价之宝…胜利从来偏爱千锤百炼的军队和千锤百炼的军人。(p13) 2、为了记住国耻，要记住甲午。知耻而后勇，首先要知。不对耻进行艰难沉重的思索，就不能期望勇...

